def IsUB (S : Set ℝ) (M : ℝ) : Prop := ∀ s ∈ S, s ≤ M

/-- `(S : Set ℝ) (M : ℝ) : Prop := ∀ s ∈ S, s ≤ M`

The point `M` is an upper bound of the set `S` if every element `s` in `S` satisfies `s ≤ M`.
-/
